							<a href="./posting.php?mode=quote&amp;f=10&amp;p=26955&amp;sid=8bf69ee0322f11fdfd9bf7c24f15847c" title="Ответить с цитатой" class="button icon-button quote-icon"><span>Цитата</span></a>
